{
  "stem": "14463.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To our greatest shock and surprise, a letter came from my father, from Chrzanow.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that was the first contact we had from Chrzanow.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I have got those letters.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we found out through his letters that my brother was one of the first to be taken to the school, where I was going to school, where he was going to school, with a lot of boys his age group, which was 19, 20, 19-year-old, 20-year-old.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they were taken to Germany to work.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my brother was writing to his father cards-- not letters, but cards.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And my father put the cards into his letters together and sent it us, to Korostelovka, and I've got them.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And this is priceless to me, absolutely priceless.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Shock.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was in absolute shock.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was trembling.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she was shocked.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that went on for quite some time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I got those letters and I got those cards.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I translated it to-- in English for my children so that they can understand it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that was something so incredible.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because I have got a letter from my father, who farewells me, because he knew he was going to go to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And that I've got.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And now those letters I knew by heart, every word.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I used to keep in my pocket, right through the war, even in Australia, when I was here the first, I think, six months.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I can't tell you with what-- with what holiness, you know, I look at those letters.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It's just incredible, just-- you know, what he writes in there, with so much wisdom, and with so much understanding, and with so much heart, how he foresaw what is going to happen.",
      "word_count": 33
    }
  ],
